<summary><strong>sort_integers</strong> — Sorting a large array of integers</summary>

This task reads the same deterministic fixture in every language and validates the workload with a printed checksum/result. This stresses file parsing, allocation behavior, the language's standard-library sort implementation, and raw single-process CPU throughput on a simple but realistic data-processing workload.

##### PHP

```php
<?php
function run_sort_integers(string $size, string $fixturesRoot): void {
  $path = $fixturesRoot . "/generated/sort/{$size}.txt";
  $values = array_map('intval', preg_split('/\s+/', trim(file_get_contents($path))));
